.edit-form-row { margin-bottom: 14px; }
.edit-form-row label { display: block; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.edit-form-row input, .edit-form-row textarea, .edit-form-row select { width: 100%; padding: 8px 10px; background: #0f1117; border: 1px solid #333; border-radius: 4px; color: #eee; font-size: 0.85rem; font-family: inherit; }
.edit-form-row textarea { min-height: 72px; resize: vertical; }
.edit-checkbox-group { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
.edit-checkbox-group label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; font-size: 0.8rem; cursor: pointer; }
.edit-form-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: flex-end; margin-top: 18px; }
.edit-btn { padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 4px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
.edit-btn-save { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; }
.edit-btn-cancel { background: #2d3555; color: #ccc; }
```

